&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Company&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are 17 million Americans who own rental property. Most don&#39;t want to be landlords anymore, but selling isn&#39;t a good option. Why? You&#39;d lose income and appreciation, trigger tax liabilities, kick out your tenants, have to fix up the house – the list goes on! Flock is here to help.&lt;/p&gt;
