&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring an &lt;strong&gt;Advisor Consultant &lt;/strong&gt;to build Flock&#39;s advisor channel. If you&#39;ve spent 1–4 years as an internal wholesaler or internal sales consultant at an alternative investment sponsor, you know exactly what this is. But our product is different: a direct 721 exchange into a diversified residential portfolio is a story most RIAs haven&#39;t heard. You won&#39;t be the fourth DST wholesaler to call this week.&lt;/p&gt;
