&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maintain pipeline integrity:&lt;/strong&gt; Keep your Salesforce hygiene tight so the team has a real-time picture of what&#39;s working and what isn&#39;t.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feed field intelligence back to the team:&lt;/strong&gt; Surface objections you&#39;re hearing, competitive products advisors mention, gaps in your collateral. The feedback loop from you to product/marketing is tight—changes happen in days, not quarters.&lt;/li&gt;
